Hill!

120
00:08:18,081 --> 00:08:19,361
能听到吗？
Do you CODY?

121
00:08:20,084 --> 00:08:21,411
巴顿叛变了
Barton has turned.

122
00:08:22,003 --> 00:08:22,879


123
00:08:34,473 --> 00:08:37,307
