125
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:15,925
快走，别管它了，快走！
Okay, let's go. No, leave it. Go!

126
00:09:32,405 --> 00:09:34,527
楼上撤离完毕了，长官，你得走了
We're clear upstairs, sir. You need to go.

127
