Director Fury, do you copy?

132
00:11:09,877 --> 00:11:12,165
宇宙立方已落入敌手
The Tesseract is with a hostile force.

133
00:11:12,422 --> 00:11:14,828
有人受伤，希尔，你那边呢？
I have men down. Hill?

134
00:11:15,174 --> 00:11:17,047
还有很多人被埋
A lot of men still under.

135
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:18,967
不清楚有多少生还者
I don't know how many survivors.

136
00:11:19,177 --> 00:11:20,339
发布命令
Sound a general call.

137
00:11:20,554 --> 00:11:22,261
所有没参加救援工作的人员
I want every living soul not working rescue

138
00:11:22,389 --> 00:11:23,384
都去寻找那个箱子
looking for that briefcase.

139
00:11:23,598 --> 00:11:24,629
收到
Roger that.

140
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:28,134
古逊，赶回基地，这是七级事件
Coulson, get back to base. This is a Level Seven.

141
00:11:29,229 --> 00:11:30,806
我们的战争
As of right now,

142
00:11:31,022 --> 00:11:32,480
就此开始
we are at war.

143
00:11:34,192 --> 00:11:35,472
