Tell Lermentov we don't need him

165
00:13:09,162 --> 00:13:12,744
还轮不到他来插手
to move the tanks.

166
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:16,329
他已是明日黄花了
Tell him he is out.

167
00:13:16,753 --> 00:13:18,377
不过
Well...

168
