I missed you, too.

697
00:44:59,686 --> 00:45:01,353
我像是跟你开玩笑的吗？
Do I look to be in a gaming mood?

698
00:45:02,063 --> 00:45:03,437
你应该感谢我
You should thank me.

699
00:45:03,898 --> 00:45:05,937
彩虹桥已毁，奥丁汇聚了多少暗能
With the Bifrost gone, how much dark energy

700
00:45:06,151 --> 00:45:08,901
才把你传送到
did the Allfather have to muster to conjure you here

701
00:45:09,112 --> 00:45:10,486
你心爱的地球上？
to your precious Earth?

702
00:45:10,793 --> 00:45:12,169


703
