I thought you dead.

704
00:45:17,537 --> 00:45:18,947
你为我哀悼了？
Did you mourn?

705
00:45:19,414 --> 00:45:21,204
我们都哀悼了，我们的父王…
We all did. Our father...

706
00:45:21,541 --> 00:45:24,457
你的父王
Your father.

707
00:45:26,337 --> 00:45:29,207
他把我的身世告诉你了，不是吗？
He did tell you my true parentage, did he not?

708
00:45:31,760 --> 00:45:34,000
我们从小一块长大
We were raised together.

709
00:45:34,220 --> 00:45:36,841
一起嬉戏，一同打闹
We played together, we fought together.

710
00:45:37,348 --> 00:45:38,546
你都不记得了吗？
Do you remember none of that?

711
00:45:38,767 --> 00:45:40,723
我只记得阴影
I remember a shadow.

712
00:45:42,228 --> 00:45:45,264
我活在你伟大所投射的阴影中
Living in the shade of your greatness.

713
00:45:45,982 --> 00:45:48,602
