that can't be controlled.

1148
01:08:39,805 --> 01:08:40,919
所以要控制立方？
Like you controlled the Cube?

1149
01:08:41,056 --> 01:08:42,300
正因为你开发立方
Your work with the Tesseract

1150
01:08:42,433 --> 01:08:45,005
才招致洛基等人到来
is what drew Loki to it, and his allies.

1151
01:08:45,144 --> 01:08:46,518
你已经向九大领域传达一个信息
It is a signal to all the realms

1152
01:08:46,645 --> 01:08:49,314
宣布地球已经准备好高规格战斗
that the Earth is ready for a higher form of war.

1153
01:08:49,440 --> 01:08:50,518
高规格战斗
A higher form?

1154
01:08:50,649 --> 01:08:51,644
你逼人在先
You forced our hand.

1155
01:08:51,776 --> 01:08:52,770
我们总要有对策
We had to come up with something.

1156
01:08:52,902 --> 01:08:53,896
用核武器镇压
A nuclear deterrent.

1157
01:08:54,028 --> 01:08:56,019
这总能避免大动干戈
Because that always calms everything right down.

1158
01:08:56,155 --> 01:08:58,526
