I'm sorry, isn't everything?

1162
01:09:04,163 --> 01:09:06,036
还以为人类已经高度文明了
I thought humans were more evolved than this.

1163
01:09:06,165 --> 01:09:09,035
再怎么也不会跑到尊星球打仗啦
Excuse me, did we come to your planet and blow stuff up?

1164
01:09:09,168 --> 01:09:11,041
你们如此不信任你的战友
You treat your champions with such mistrust.

1165
01:09:11,170 --> 01:09:12,628
你们好天真啊
Are you boys really that naïve?

1166
01:09:12,755 --> 01:09:14,628
神盾局监视潜在危险
S.H.I.E.L.D. monitors potential threats.

1167
01:09:14,757 --> 01:09:16,036
美国队长也是潜在威胁?
Captain America's on threat watch?

1168
01:09:16,175 --> 01:09:17,170
我们都是
We all are.

1169
01:09:17,301 --> 01:09:18,711
你也在监视列表上？
Wait, you're on that list?

1170
01:09:18,844 --> 01:09:20,385
你在强忍怒气吗？
Are you above or below angry bees?

1171
01:09:20,513 --> 01:09:22,635
史塔，你试试再耍嘴皮…
Stark, so help me God, if you make one more wisecrack...

1172
