Number three engine is down.

1247
01:13:04,110 --> 01:13:05,105
我们受袭
We've been hit.

1248
01:13:05,236 --> 01:13:06,398
- 能否重运作？ - 三号引擎着火
- Can they get it running? - Fire in engine three!

1249
01:13:06,529 --> 01:13:07,524
具体如何
Talk to me.

1250
01:13:07,655 --> 01:13:09,279
涡轮似乎完好
Turbine looks mostly intact

1251
01:13:09,407 --> 01:13:12,819
但在空中无法修复机件
but it's impossible to get out there to make repairs while we're in the air.

1252
01:13:12,952 --> 01:13:15,489
再多个引擎坏掉，就会坠机
If we lose one more engine, we won't be.

1253
01:13:15,622 --> 01:13:17,613
要派人出去修复引擎
Somebody's got to get outside and patch that engine.

1254
01:13:17,749 --> 01:13:19,456
- 史塔，收到吗？ - 我马上去
- Stark, you copy that? - I'm on it.

1255
01:13:19,584 --> 01:13:22,869
古逊，关押区实施防御封锁
Coulson, initiate defensive lockdown in the detention section

1256
