布斯？
Bruce?

1272
01:14:11,760 --> 01:14:15,424
冷静，否则正中洛基下怀
You got to fight it. This is just what Loki wants.

1273
01:14:16,807 --> 01:14:17,837
听着，会没事的
We're going to be okay. Listen to me.

1274
01:14:17,975 --> 01:14:18,970
你受伤了吗
Are you hurt?

1275
01:14:22,271 --> 01:14:24,476
会没事的
We're going to be okay. All right?

1276
01:14:24,606 --> 01:14:27,357
我以性命担保，我会救你出去
I swear on my life, I will get you out of this.

1277
01:14:27,484 --> 01:14:28,859
你可以从此不问世事
You will walk away and never ever...

1278
01:14:28,986 --> 01:14:31,061
以你性命担保？
Your life?

1279
