01:00:59,050 --> 01:01:02,010
所以 如果非要说的话 其实我在这里也怪你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So, if anything, it's kinda your fault that I'm here.

926
01:01:02,010 --> 01:01:03,430
-你说什么 -我收回
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What did you just say? - I take that back.

927
01:01:03,430 --> 01:01:04,980
现在我已经在太空里了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And now, I'm here in space.

928
01:01:04,980 --> 01:01:07,650
是啊 就在我最不想让你来的地方
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, right where I didn't want you to be.

929
01:01:07,650 --> 01:01:09,860
这不是康尼岛 不是出外勤
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This isn't Coney Island. This isn't a field trip.

930
01:01:09,860 --> 01:01:10,980
这儿可是有去无回
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is a one-way ticket.

931
01:01:10,980 --> 01:01:12,820
你明白了吗 别假装你已经想清楚了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You hear me? Don't pretend you thought this through.

932
01:01:12,820 --> 01:01:13,940
我确实想清楚了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I did think this through.

933
01:01:13,940 --> 01:01:15,740
你怎么可能想清楚
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You could not have possibly thought this through.

934
01:01:15,740 --> 01:01:17,280
如果整个社区都没了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You can't be a friendly neighborhood Spider-Man...

935
01:01:17,280 --> 01:01:18,950
我如何当个友好的社区蜘蛛侠
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if there's no neighborhood.

936
01:01:21,080 --> 01:01:22,240
好吧 好像这么说也不对
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay, that didn't really make sense,

937
01:01:22,240 --> 01:01:23,700
但你知道我想表达什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but you know what I'm trying to say.

938
01:01:25,790 --> 01:01:29,710
好吧 我们现在有个状况
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on. We got a situation.

939
01:01:29,710 --> 01:01:30,790
看见下面那个人了吗 他有麻烦了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See him down there? He's in trouble.

940
01:01:30,790 --> 01:01:31,840
你有什么计划吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's your plan?

941
01:01:31,840 --> 01:01:32,960
-说 -呃
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Go. - Um...

942
01:01:33,710 --> 01:01:35,300
好吧 好吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay, okay... Uh...

943
01:01:35,300 --> 01:01:38,720
你看过一部非常老的电影吗 叫《异形》
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay. Did you ever see this really old movie, Aliens?

944
01:01:42,220 --> 01:01:45,140
很痛苦吧 是不是
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Painful, aren't they?

945
01:01:45,140 --> 01:01:48,810
这些针最初是在显微外科手术中使用的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}They were originally designed for microsurgery.

946
01:01:48,810 --> 01:01:50,900
而其中的任意一根
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And any one of them...

947
01:01:55,990 --> 01:01:58,820
都能瞬间结束你朋友的生命
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}could end your friend's life in an instant.

948
01:01:58,820 --> 01:02:00,450
实话实说 他其实不是我的朋友
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I gotta tell you, he's not really my friend.

949
01:02:00,450 --> 01:02:03,160
救他的命其实只是出于职业素养而已
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Saving his life is more of a professional courtesy.

950
01:02:04,990 --> 01:02:07,710
你还没救成呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You've saved nothing.

951
01:02:07,710 --> 01:02:09,790
你的力量和我相比
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your powers are inconsequential

952
01:02:09,790 --> 01:02:11,290
根本不值一提
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}compared to mine.

953
01:02:11,290 --> 01:02:13,000
是啊 但那孩子看的电影更多
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, but the kid's seen more movies.

954
01:02:27,140 --> 01:02:29,270
太棒了 等等 那些是什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yes! Wait. What are those?

955
01:02:44,990 --> 01:02:46,740
嗨 咱们还没有正式见过面呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hey, we haven't officially met.

956
01:02:48,000 --> 01:02:49,040
好吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Cool.

957
01:02:51,040 --> 01:02:52,540
我们要调转航向
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We gotta turn this ship around.

958
01:02:52,540 --> 01:02:54,880
是啊 现在你倒是想逃了 真是一个好计划
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, now he wants to run. Great plan.

959
01:02:54,880 --> 01:02:56,340
不 我想保护原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I want to protect the stone.

960
01:02:56,340 --> 01:02:57,760
我还想听你感谢我呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I want you to thank me.

961
01:02:57,760 --> 01:02:59,300
现在说吧 我听着呢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Now, go ahead. I'm listening.

962
01:02:59,300 --> 01:03:02,220
谢你什么 差点把我炸进太空吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For what? Nearly blasting me into space?

963
01:03:02,220 --> 01:03:04,550
是谁刚刚救了你这个大魔术师啊 是我
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Who just saved your magical ass? Me.

964
01:03:04,550 --> 01:03:05,390
我真的不知道
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I seriously don't know

965
01:03:05,390 --> 01:03:06,560
你是怎么把你的大脑袋塞进那个头盔里的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}how you fit your head into that helmet.

966
01:03:06,560 --> 01:03:09,390
承认吧 我叫你闪开的时候你就应该照做
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Admit it, you should've ducked out when I told you to.

967
01:03:09,390 --> 01:03:11,140
我想要你老实待着 而你拒绝了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I tried to bench you. You refused.

968
01:03:11,140 --> 01:03:13,230
我不像你生命中的其他人 我不听命于你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Unlike everyone else in your life, I don't work for you.

969
01:03:13,230 --> 01:03:14,940
正因为你不听话
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And due to that fact,

970
01:03:14,940 --> 01:03:16,360
我们现在在一个会飞的甜甜圈里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}we're now in a flying doughnut...

971
01:03:16,360 --> 01:03:18,230
离地球几百万里远 还没有后援
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}billions of miles from Earth with no backup.

972
01:03:18,230 --> 01:03:20,280
-我是后援 -不 你是偷跑上来的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I'm backup. - No, you're a stowaway.

973
01:03:20,280 --> 01:03:21,360
大人说话 小孩别插嘴
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The adults are talking.

974
01:03:21,360 --> 01:03:24,240
对不起 我搞不清楚你们的关系了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry, I'm confused as to the relationship here.

975
01:03:24,240 --> 01:03:26,080
他是谁 你的保镖吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What is he, your ward?

976
01:03:26,080 --> 01:03:27,450
不
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.

977
01:03:27,450 --> 01:03:29,500
-我是彼得 -斯特兰奇博士
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- I'm Peter, by the way. - Doctor Strange.

978
01:03:29,500 --> 01:03:31,250
要用艺名啊
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, you're using our made-up names. Um...

979
01:03:32,250 --> 01:03:34,380
那我是蜘蛛侠
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm Spider-Man, then.

980
01:03:34,380 --> 01:03:36,040
这架飞船正在自动矫正航线
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This ship is self-correcting its course.

981
01:03:36,040 --> 01:03:37,170
现在是自动驾驶模式
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thing's on autopilot.

982
01:03:37,170 --> 01:03:39,090
我们能控制它吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can we control it?

983
01:03:39,090 --> 01:03:41,010
载我们回家
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Fly us home?

984
01:03:44,010 --> 01:03:45,140
-史塔克 -怎么了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Stark? - Yeah.

985
01:03:45,140 --> 01:03:46,470
你能带我们回去吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Can you get us home?

986
01:03:46,470 --> 01:03:47,890
我听到你的话了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, I heard you.

987
01:03:49,100 --> 01:03:51,480
我只是在想 我不太确定我们应该回去
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm thinking I'm not so sure we should.

988
01:03:52,230 --> 01:03:53,890
无论如何
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Under no circumstances

989
01:03:53,890 --> 01:03:56,440
我们都不能把时间原石送到灭霸的手中
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}can we bring the Time Stone to Thanos.

990
01:03:56,440 --> 01:03:57,860
我觉得你还没有
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I don't think you quite understand

991
01:03:57,860 --> 01:03:58,770
搞清楚现在的局势
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}what's at stake here.

992
01:03:58,770 --> 01:04:01,400
什么 不 是你不懂
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What? No. It's you who doesn't understand...

993
01:04:01,400 --> 01:04:04,320
自从他派军到纽约时起
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that Thanos has been inside my head for six years.

994
01:04:04,320 --> 01:04:06,070
灭霸已经在我的脑海中盘踞六年了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Since he sent an army to New York

995
01:04:06,070 --> 01:04:07,830
而现在他回来了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and now he's back.

996
01:04:07,830 --> 01:04:09,910
而我不知道应该做什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And I don't know what to do.

997
01:04:09,910 --> 01:04:11,040
所以我不确定
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I'm not so sure

998
01:04:11,040 --> 01:04:13,080
这场战役是在我们还是他的地盘上打更好
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if it's a better plan to fight him on our turf or his...

999
01:04:13,080 --> 01:04:16,920
但他们的所作所为 他们的能力 你都看见了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}but you saw what they did, what they can do.

1000
01:04:16,920 --> 01:04:19,210
至少在他的地盘上 可以打他个措手不及
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At least on his turf, he's not expecting it.

1001
01:04:19,210 --> 01:04:22,130
所以我说 我们将战火引到他那儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I say we take the fight to him.

1002
01:04:22,130 --> 01:04:23,130
博士
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Doctor.

1003
01:04:24,930 --> 01:04:26,470
你同意吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you concur?

1004
01:04:29,010 --> 01:04:31,470
好吧 史塔克 我们去找他
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, Stark. We go to him.

1005
01:04:32,560 --> 01:04:34,940
但你必须要明白
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But you have to understand...

1006
01:04:34,940 --> 01:04:36,520
如果我需要在救你 还有那个孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}if it comes to saving you

1007
01:04:36,520 --> 01:04:39,230
和时间原石中做选择的话
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}or the kid or the Time Stone...

1008
01:04:39,230 --> 01:04:42,990
我会毫不犹豫地放弃你们俩的生命
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I will not hesitate to let either of you die.

1009
01:04:42,990 --> 01:04:47,160
我不能失去原石 整个宇宙的希望都在它身上
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I can't, because the universe depends on it.

1010
01:04:47,160 --> 01:04:50,080
很好 提前说清楚道德标准
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nice. Good, moral compass.

1011
01:04:51,330 --> 01:04:52,910
那就这样说定了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We're straight.

1012
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:55,410
好了 孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, kid.

1013
01:04:56,670 --> 01:04:57,880
你正式是复仇者的一员了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're an Avenger now.

1014
01:05:34,370 --> 01:05:36,580
我觉得你可能饿了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you might be hungry.

1015
01:05:48,720 --> 01:05:50,510
我一直恨那把椅子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I always hated that chair.

1016
01:05:50,510 --> 01:05:53,260
我听说了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I've been told.

1017
01:05:53,260 --> 01:05:57,230
即便这样 我也希望你有一天能坐上它
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Even so, I'd hoped you'd sit in it one day.

1018
01:05:58,020 --> 01:05:59,440
我恨这个房间
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hated this room.

1019
01:06:00,350 --> 01:06:01,730
这架飞船
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This ship.

1020
01:06:01,730 --> 01:06:03,570
我恨我的人生
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I hated my life.

1021
01:06:08,070 --> 01:06:10,280
你也跟我说过了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You told me that too.

1022
01:06:13,410 --> 01:06:14,910
每一天
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Every day.

1023
01:06:17,580 --> 01:06:19,540
我听了近二十年
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For almost 20 years.

1024
01:06:22,170 --> 01:06:24,500
你带走我时 我还只是个孩子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I was a child when you took me.

1025
01:06:25,420 --> 01:06:26,670
我救了你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I saved you.

1026
01:06:30,260 --> 01:06:31,090
不
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No.

1027
01:06:32,680 --> 01:06:36,430
不是 我们曾经快乐地生活在我的母星上
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No. We were happy on my home planet.

1028
01:06:36,430 --> 01:06:38,180
每天在饥饿中入睡
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Going to bed hungry...

1029
01:06:38,180 --> 01:06:40,100
以拾荒为生
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}scrounging for scraps.

1030
01:06:40,100 --> 01:06:43,060
你的星球已经在崩溃的边缘了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your planet was on the brink of collapse.

1031
01:06:43,060 --> 01:06:45,480
是我拯救了那一切
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm the one who stopped that.

1032
01:06:45,480 --> 01:06:47,490
你知道后来发生了什么吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do you know what's happened since then?

1033
01:06:47,490 --> 01:06:49,700
新生儿们
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The children born...

1034
01:06:49,700 --> 01:06:53,320
在蓝天下过着富足的生活
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}have known nothing but full bellies and clear skies.

1035
01:06:53,320 --> 01:06:54,530
那里成了天堂
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a paradise.

1036
01:06:57,290 --> 01:06:59,290
因为你杀掉了星球上一半的人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Because you murdered half the planet.

1037
01:06:59,290 --> 01:07:02,330
那只是为了救赎而付出的小小代价而已
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A small price to pay for salvation.

1038
01:07:02,330 --> 01:07:03,460
你疯了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're insane.

1039
01:07:03,460 --> 01:07:05,590
小家伙 这是一道简单的算术题
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Little one, it's a simple calculus.

1040
01:07:05,590 --> 01:07:09,050
宇宙是有限的 它的资源也是有限的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This universe is finite, its resources finite.

1041
01:07:09,050 --> 01:07:13,390
如果对生命不加以约束 它最终将走向消亡
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}If life is left unchecked, life will cease to exist.

1042
01:07:13,390 --> 01:07:14,600
它需要矫正
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It needs correction.

1043
01:07:14,600 --> 01:07:16,100
你不能妄下定论
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You don't know that!

1044
01:07:17,520 --> 01:07:20,390
我是唯一一个看清的人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm the only one who knows that.

1045
01:07:20,390 --> 01:07:24,560
至少我是唯一愿意付出行动的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}At least, I'm the only one with the will to act on it.

1046
01:07:26,230 --> 01:07:27,230
曾经
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For a time...

1047
01:07:29,690 --> 01:07:34,120
与我并肩战斗的你
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}you had that same will...

1048
01:07:35,570 --> 01:07:38,120
也有着共同的信仰
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}as you fought by my side.

1049
01:07:38,830 --> 01:07:40,040
女儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Daughter.

1050
01:07:40,660 --> 01:07:42,500
我不是你的女儿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not your daughter.

1051
01:07:45,040 --> 01:07:47,670
我痛恨你教给我的一切东西
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everything I hate about myself you taught me.

1052
01:07:48,500 --> 01:07:50,090
正是这些
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And, in doing so,

1053
01:07:50,090 --> 01:07:52,300
让你成为银河中最勇敢无畏的女人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}made you the fiercest woman in the galaxy.

1054
01:07:55,220 --> 01:07:58,100
所以我当时才派你去寻找灵魂原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's why I trusted you to find the Soul Stone.

1055
01:08:01,390 --> 01:08:04,270
抱歉我让你失望了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm sorry I disappointed you.

1056
01:08:05,400 --> 01:08:08,070
我的确很失望
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am disappointed.

1057
01:08:08,070 --> 01:08:10,440
但不是因为你没有找到
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But not because you didn't find it.

1058
01:08:14,200 --> 01:08:15,700
而是因为你找到了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But because you did.

1059
01:08:17,280 --> 01:08:19,080
却对我说谎了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And you lied.

1060
01:08:36,180 --> 01:08:37,260
星云
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Nebula.

1061
01:08:44,480 --> 01:08:45,850
不要这样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't do this.

1062
01:08:45,900 --> 01:08:47,310
不久以前
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Some time ago,

1063
01:08:47,310 --> 01:08:50,190
你妹妹潜入这架飞船来刺杀我
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}your sister snuck aboard this ship to kill me.

1064
01:08:50,230 --> 01:08:51,280
求求你 别这样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Please don't do this.

1065
01:08:51,280 --> 01:08:53,530
她差点就成功了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}And very nearly succeeded.

1066
01:08:54,240 --> 01:08:55,610
所以我把她带到这里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So I brought her here.

1067
01:08:57,240 --> 01:08:58,450
来谈一谈
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To talk.

1068
01:09:06,170 --> 01:09:08,500
停下 住手
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stop. Stop it.

1069
01:09:14,420 --> 01:09:17,260
我以我的性命起誓
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I swear to you on my life.

1070
01:09:17,260 --> 01:09:19,510
我没有找到灵魂原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I never found the Soul Stone.

