1214
01:18:50,040 --> 01:18:51,630
你还好吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You all right?

1215
01:18:52,460 --> 01:18:54,250
好险
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That was close.

1216
01:18:55,760 --> 01:18:57,340
我欠你一次
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I owe you one.

1217
01:18:57,340 --> 01:18:59,470
我提前说一句
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let me just say, if aliens

1218
01:18:59,470 --> 01:19:01,430
如果异形在我胸腔里产了卵
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}wind up implanting eggs in my chest or something...

1219
01:19:01,430 --> 01:19:02,470
然后我吃了你们其中一个 那就抱歉了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I eat one of you, I'm sorry.

1220
01:19:02,470 --> 01:19:05,180
在接下来的旅途中
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I do not want another single pop culture reference

1221
01:19:05,180 --> 01:19:06,930
我都不想再听到你说任何流行文化的梗了 你明白了吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}out of you for the rest of the trip. You understand?

1222
01:19:06,930 --> 01:19:08,310
我想说的是 有什么东西过来了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm trying to say that something is coming.

1223
01:19:15,820 --> 01:19:16,900
灭霸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Thanos!

1224
01:19:37,760 --> 01:19:39,840
天哪 求你别在我身体里产卵
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Whoa, whoa, whoa! Please don't put your eggs in me!

1225
01:19:41,180 --> 01:19:43,720
去死吧 小丑
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stay down, clown.

1226
01:19:48,890 --> 01:19:50,980
受死吧 死亡之毯
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Die, blanket of death!

1227
01:19:56,900 --> 01:19:59,860
所有人待在原地 冷静一下
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Everybody stay where you are. Chill the eff out.

1228
01:20:01,030 --> 01:20:03,030
我只问你一次
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna ask you this one time.

1229
01:20:03,820 --> 01:20:05,160
卡魔拉在哪里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is Gamora?

1230
01:20:05,160 --> 01:20:07,990
我问你一个更好的问题 卡魔拉是谁
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah. I'll do you one better. Who's Gamora?

1231
01:20:07,990 --> 01:20:10,960
我来问一个更好的问题 为什么要抓卡魔拉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll do you one better. Why is Gamora?

1232
01:20:10,960 --> 01:20:12,960
告诉我那女孩在哪里 不然我发誓
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me where the girl is or I swear to you

1233
01:20:12,960 --> 01:20:14,210
我会把这个小怪物炸成薯条
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm gonna French fry this little freak.

1234
01:20:14,210 --> 01:20:17,840
谁怕谁 你给我的人一枪 我就给他一炮 来啊
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Let's do it. You shoot my guy and I'll blast him. Let's go!

1235
01:20:17,840 --> 01:20:20,420
动手 奎尔 我能受得住
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Do it, Quill! I can take it.

1236
01:20:20,420 --> 01:20:22,550
-不 他受不住的 -她说得对 你受不住
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- No, he can't take it! - She's right. You can't.

1237
01:20:22,550 --> 01:20:24,930
哦 是吗 你不打算告诉我她在哪里是吗 没关系
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, yeah? You don't wanna tell me where she is? That's fine.

1238
01:20:24,930 --> 01:20:26,050
我会干掉你们三个
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'll kill all three of you

1239
01:20:26,050 --> 01:20:28,060
然后亲自去拷问灭霸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and I'll beat it out of Thanos myself.

1240
01:20:28,060 --> 01:20:29,100
就从你开始
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Starting with you.

1241
01:20:29,100 --> 01:20:30,060
等等 等等 灭霸
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Wait, what, Thanos?

1242
01:20:30,060 --> 01:20:32,890
好了 我就问你一遍
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, let me ask you this one time.

1243
01:20:32,890 --> 01:20:34,560
你效忠于何人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What master do you serve?

1244
01:20:34,560 --> 01:20:36,060
我效忠于何人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What master do I serve?

1245
01:20:36,060 --> 01:20:37,400
我该怎么说 效忠于"耶稣"吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What am I supposed to say, "Jesus"?

1246
01:20:38,400 --> 01:20:39,280
你是地球人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're from Earth.

1247
01:20:39,280 --> 01:20:40,190
我才不是 我密苏里人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I'm not from Earth, I'm from Missouri.

1248
01:20:40,190 --> 01:20:42,150
密苏里就在地球上 蠢货
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, that's on Earth, dipshit.

1249
01:20:42,150 --> 01:20:43,320
那你们为什么要找我们麻烦
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What are you hassling us for?

1250
01:20:43,320 --> 01:20:45,110
所以你们不是和灭霸一伙的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So you're not with Thanos?

1251
01:20:45,530 --> 01:20:48,030
和灭霸一伙？
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}With Thanos?

1252
01:20:48,030 --> 01:20:50,830
才不是 我是来杀灭霸的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}No, I'm here to kill Thanos.

1253
01:20:50,830 --> 01:20:53,370
他绑走了我女朋友 等等 你们到底是谁
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}He took my girl. Wait, who are you?

1254
01:20:53,370 --> 01:20:55,210
-我们是复仇者联盟 哥们儿 -哦
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- We're the Avengers, man. - Oh.

1255
01:20:55,210 --> 01:20:57,590
你们就是索尔跟我们说的那些人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're the ones Thor told us about.

1256
01:20:57,590 --> 01:20:59,040
你认识索尔
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know Thor?

1257
01:20:59,040 --> 01:21:00,000
对
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah.

1258
01:21:00,000 --> 01:21:02,880
高个子 长得不帅 心理还有问题
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tall guy, not that good-looking, needed saving.

1259
01:21:02,880 --> 01:21:04,430
他现在在哪里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is he now?

1260
01:21:19,440 --> 01:21:21,480
这就是计划吗 我们带着一块砖去拍他
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This is the plan? We're gonna hit him with a brick?

1261
01:21:21,480 --> 01:21:22,860
这只是个模具
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's a mold.

1262
01:21:23,440 --> 01:21:25,450
王之武器
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A king's weapon.

1263
01:21:25,450 --> 01:21:28,410
本是阿斯加德之最
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Meant to be the greatest in Asgard.

1264
01:21:28,410 --> 01:21:31,450
理论上 它甚至可以召唤彩虹桥
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In theory, it could even summon the Bifrost.

1265
01:21:31,450 --> 01:21:33,000
它有名字吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did it have a name?

1266
01:21:34,210 --> 01:21:35,920
风暴之锤
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Stormbreaker.

1267
01:21:35,920 --> 01:21:37,000
有点中二
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}That's a bit much.

1268
01:21:39,040 --> 01:21:40,130
所以我们要怎么把它造出来
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So how do we make it?

1269
01:21:41,960 --> 01:21:44,130
你要重新燃起熔炉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You'll have to restart the forge.

1270
01:21:45,130 --> 01:21:47,300
唤醒一颗濒死星球的心脏
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Awaken the heart of a dying star.

1271
01:21:49,970 --> 01:21:52,470
兔子 去启动分离舱
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Rabbit, fire up the pod.

1272
01:21:56,230 --> 01:21:58,310
这星球到底经历了什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The hell happened to this planet?

1273
01:21:58,310 --> 01:22:00,230
偏离了轴线八度
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's eight degrees off its axis.

1274
01:22:00,230 --> 01:22:02,400
引力到处都是
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gravitational pull is all over the place.

1275
01:22:03,650 --> 01:22:07,490
是啊 我们有一个优势 他会来找我们的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, we got one advantage. He's coming to us.

1276
01:22:07,490 --> 01:22:10,320
我们就利用这点 好了 我有个计划
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We'll use it. All right, I have a plan.

1277
01:22:10,320 --> 01:22:11,660
或者至少是初步计划
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Or at least the beginnings of one.

1278
01:22:11,660 --> 01:22:13,160
很简单 我们把他引过来
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It's pretty simple. We draw him in,

1279
01:22:13,160 --> 01:22:14,500
合力擒住他 拿走我们需要的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}pin him down, get what we need.

1280
01:22:14,500 --> 01:22:16,290
我们明显不能和这家伙周旋纠缠
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Definitely don't wanna dance with this guy.

1281
01:22:16,290 --> 01:22:18,000
我们只需要拿到手套
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We just want the gauntlet.

1282
01:22:18,000 --> 01:22:20,330
你是在打哈欠吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Are you yawning?

1283
01:22:20,330 --> 01:22:22,630
在我解释计划的这个时候 哈
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}In the middle of this, while I'm breaking it down? Huh?

1284
01:22:22,630 --> 01:22:24,460
你有听到我说了什么吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Did you hear what I said?

1285
01:22:24,460 --> 01:22:27,010
在你说“我们需要一个计划”之后 我就没再听了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I stopped listening after you said, "We need a plan."

1286
01:22:27,010 --> 01:22:28,050
好吧 光头先生沉浸在自己的世界里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay, Mr. Clean is on his own page.

1287
01:22:28,050 --> 01:22:31,180
“别搞砸事情”不是他们的作风
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See, "Not winging it" Isn't really what they do.

1288
01:22:31,180 --> 01:22:32,930
呃 那他们的实际作风是什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Uh, what exactly is it that they do?

1289
01:22:32,930 --> 01:22:34,520
拉风头 抢仇恨
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Kick names, take ass.

1290
01:22:34,520 --> 01:22:35,930
是的 没错
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Yeah, that's right.

1291
01:22:42,520 --> 01:22:44,320
算了 先都聚过来吧 拜托了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, just get over here, please.

1292
01:22:44,320 --> 01:22:46,360
爵士先生 你能让你的人围过来吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Mr. Lord, can you get your folks to circle up?

1293
01:22:46,360 --> 01:22:48,530
什么“爵士先生” 叫我星爵就行
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}"Mr. Lord." Star-Lord is fine.

1294
01:22:51,280 --> 01:22:52,660
我们要联合起来
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We gotta coalesce.

1295
01:22:52,660 --> 01:22:54,490
因为如果我们全都迎面而上 是勇气可嘉的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}'Cause if all we come at him with is a plucky attitude...

1296
01:22:54,490 --> 01:22:57,040
大哥 别跟我们说什么勇气
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Dude, don't call us plucky.

1297
01:22:57,040 --> 01:22:58,540
我们不懂那是什么意思
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We don't know what it means.

1298
01:22:58,540 --> 01:23:01,330
好吧 我们都很乐观 没错 我喜欢你的计划
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}All right, we're optimistic, yes. I like your plan.

1299
01:23:01,330 --> 01:23:04,040
不过它很烂 所以让我来定计划
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Except it sucks, so let me do the plan...

1300
01:23:04,040 --> 01:23:06,090
这样我们的计划没准会很棒
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}and that way it might be really good.

1301
01:23:06,090 --> 01:23:08,220
告诉他你是怎么通过尬舞拯救宇宙的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell him about the dance-off to save the universe.

1302
01:23:08,220 --> 01:23:10,430
-什么尬舞 -没什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- What dance-off? - It's nothing.

1303
01:23:10,410 --> 01:23:13,530
《浑身是劲》：1984年上映的美国剧情电影

1304
01:23:10,430 --> 01:23:11,590
就像《浑身是劲》电影里那样吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Like in Footloose, the movie?

1305
01:23:11,590 --> 01:23:13,550
没错 就跟《浑身是劲》一样
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Exactly like Footloose.

1306
01:23:13,550 --> 01:23:15,260
它还是史上最棒的电影吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Is it still the greatest movie in history?

1307
01:23:15,260 --> 01:23:16,520
它从来就不是
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It never was.

1308
01:23:16,520 --> 01:23:17,600
别让他来劲 好吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't encourage this, all right?

1309
01:23:17,580 --> 01:23:20,620
飞侠哥顿：1980年美国动作科幻电影中的人物

1310
01:23:17,600 --> 01:23:19,100
-好吧 -这位飞侠哥顿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Okay. - We're getting no help

1311
01:23:19,100 --> 01:23:20,640
-显然帮不上我们什么 -飞侠哥顿
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- from Flash Gordon here. - Flash Gordon?

1312
01:23:20,640 --> 01:23:22,400
顺便一说 那可是称赞
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}By the way, that's a compliment.

1313
01:23:22,400 --> 01:23:24,150
别忘了 我是半个人类
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Don't forget, I'm half human.

1314
01:23:24,150 --> 01:23:25,570
所以那一半的我是蠢的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}So that 50% of me that's stupid...

1315
01:23:26,730 --> 01:23:28,070
而你们就是百分百的蠢
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}that's 100% you.

1316
01:23:28,070 --> 01:23:29,360
你的数学真令我震惊
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Your math is blowing my mind.

1317
01:23:29,360 --> 01:23:30,570
打扰一下
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Excuse me.

1318
01:23:31,570 --> 01:23:35,120
但你们的朋友经常那样吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But does your friend often do that?

1319
01:23:36,450 --> 01:23:38,700
斯特兰奇 你还好吗
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Strange, we all right?

1320
01:23:49,130 --> 01:23:50,260
你回来了 你没事
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're back. You're all right.

1321
01:23:50,260 --> 01:23:52,470
-嗨 -嘿 刚刚是怎么回事
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- Hi. - Hey, what was that?

1322
01:23:52,470 --> 01:23:57,100
我顺着时间前进 去浏览未来的可能
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I went forward in time to view alternate futures.

1323
01:23:57,100 --> 01:23:58,600
去看即将来临的大战
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}To see all the possible outcomes

1324
01:23:58,600 --> 01:24:00,480
所有可能发生的结局
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}of the coming conflict.

1325
01:24:01,270 --> 01:24:02,690
你看到了多少种结局
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How many did you see?

1326
01:24:02,690 --> 01:24:05,110
一千四百万六百零五种
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}14,000,605.

1327
01:24:06,610 --> 01:24:08,150
我们赢了多少次
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How many did we win?

1328
01:24:12,780 --> 01:24:14,120
一次
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}One.

1329
01:24:26,690 --> 01:24:30,900
{\fn方正宋黑简体\blur0.4\c&HC8C8C8&\fs90\b0\fad(1200,1200)\pos(640,252.533)}沃米尔星

1330
01:24:35,800 --> 01:24:39,010
为了你妹妹小命
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The stone had better be up there.

1331
01:24:40,720 --> 01:24:42,770
原石最好在那里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}For your sister's sake.

1332
01:25:03,660 --> 01:25:08,500
欢迎 灭霸 阿拉尔斯之子
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Welcome, Thanos, son of Alars.

1333
01:25:10,550 --> 01:25:14,090
卡魔拉 灭霸之女
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Gamora, daughter of Thanos.

1334
01:25:14,090 --> 01:25:15,340
你认识我们
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You know us?

1335
01:25:15,340 --> 01:25:20,390
认识每一个来到这里的人就是我的诅咒
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}It is my curse to know all who journey here.

1336
01:25:20,390 --> 01:25:22,140
灵魂原石在哪里
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is the Soul Stone?

1337
01:25:22,680 --> 01:25:25,140
你该知道
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You should know...

1338
01:25:25,190 --> 01:25:28,270
它会让你付出可怕的代价
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}it extracts a terrible price.

1339
01:25:29,520 --> 01:25:31,190
我准备好了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I am prepared.

1340
01:25:33,570 --> 01:25:36,110
一开始 我们都这样以为
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We all think that at first.

1341
01:25:40,530 --> 01:25:42,790
但我们都错了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}We are all wrong.

1342
01:25:54,470 --> 01:25:56,880
你为什么对这个地方如此熟悉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}How is it you know this place so well?

1343
01:25:56,880 --> 01:26:01,720
一百年前 我也试图寻找无限原石
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}A lifetime ago, I, too, sought the stones.

1344
01:26:01,720 --> 01:26:04,600
甚至已经有一颗在我的手上
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I even held one in my hand.

1345
01:26:04,600 --> 01:26:08,770
但它驱逐了我 将我流放至此
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}But it cast me out, banished me here.

1346
01:26:08,770 --> 01:26:12,820
指引他人搜寻我无法拥有的珍宝
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guiding others to a treasure I cannot possess.

1347
01:26:21,580 --> 01:26:24,540
你所寻找的就在你面前
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What you seek lies in front of you.

1348
01:26:25,500 --> 01:26:27,580
你所畏惧的也是如此
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}As does what you fear.

1349
01:26:28,420 --> 01:26:30,380
这是什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What's this?

1350
01:26:30,380 --> 01:26:31,920
代价
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}The price.

1351
01:26:31,920 --> 01:26:37,630
在所有无限原石中 灵魂原石有着特殊的地位
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Soul holds a special place among the Infinity Stones.

1352
01:26:37,630 --> 01:26:41,720
可以说 它有一定的智慧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You might say it has a certain wisdom.

1353
01:26:43,220 --> 01:26:45,220
告诉我 它需要什么
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Tell me what it needs.

