现在没那么嚣张了吧
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}You're not so strong now, huh?

1564
01:51:07,690 --> 01:51:09,360
卡魔拉在哪
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Where is Gamora?

1565
01:51:09,360 --> 01:51:11,650
是我的卡魔拉
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}My Gamora.

1566
01:51:11,650 --> 01:51:13,940
你放屁
