{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on! Get some! Get some!

1591
01:53:29,290 --> 01:53:31,410
来呀 来打呀
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on! Get some!

1592
01:53:31,410 --> 01:53:34,130
-你的枪多少钱 -不卖
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}- How much for the gun? - Not for sale.

1593
01:53:34,130 --> 01:53:36,040
好吧 那手臂多少钱
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Okay. How much for the arm?

1594
01:53:37,960 --> 01:53:40,010
行吧 我会自己搞到手的
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, I'll get that arm.

1595
01:53:48,850 --> 01:53:50,140
新发型吗
