1610
01:56:21,960 --> 01:56:23,670
住手 你们休想
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Oh, no, you don't.

1611
01:56:23,670 --> 01:56:25,380
这次可不会像在纽约时一样 伙计
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This isn't gonna be like New York, pal.

1612
01:56:25,380 --> 01:56:27,970
这套装甲曾经可是把浩克都揍扁过
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}This suit's already kicked the crap outta the Hulk.

1613
01:56:27,970 --> 01:56:29,010
什么 不 不要
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}What? No! No!

1614
01:56:32,550 --> 01:56:35,310
伙计们 幻视现在需要支援
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Guys! Vision needs backup, now!

1615
01:56:37,310 --> 01:56:39,060
浩克 浩克
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hulk? Hulk,

