来呀
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Come on! Yeah!

1624
01:57:14,350 --> 01:57:16,060
拜拜咯
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}See ya!

1625
01:57:27,440 --> 01:57:30,110
浩克 我们得好好谈谈了
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}Hulk, we got a lot to figure out, pal.

1626
01:57:41,080 --> 01:57:43,000
我还以为你有多厉害呢 机器人
{\3c&H000000&\fs30}I thought you were formidable, machine.

1627
01:57:43,750 --> 01:57:46,380
