I see it within you.

118
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,780
一种不同寻常的血统
An unorthodox genealogy.

119
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:50,270
这种混血看起来特别…
A hybrid that seems particularly...

120
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,630
鲁莽
reckless.

121
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:57,640
你知道吗 我听说你们都是自以为是的混蛋
You know, they told me you people were conceited douchebags...

122
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,580
但那完全不是事实
but that isn't true at all.

123
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,190
糟糕
Oh, shit.

124
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,680
我又用错眼睛了 是吗
I'm using my wrong eye again, aren't I?

125
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:11,070
我很抱歉 我没想被你发现的
I'm sorry. That was meant to be behind your back.

126
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:14,270
他们没杀你算你走运
Count yourself blessed they didn't kill you.

127
00:12:14,380 --> 00:12:15,620
还用你说
You're telling me.

128
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,750
你想买点电池吗
You wanna buy some batteries?

129
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:34,250
好吧 我们把小秃子送去山达尔领赏吧
All right, let's get baldy to Xandar and collect that bounty.

130
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:43,450
[劲歌金曲 第二辑]

131
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:28,380
她说我父亲的那些话
That stuff about my father...

132
00:13:29,130 --> 00:13:30,470
她以为她是谁啊
Who does she think she is?

133
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:32,990
