I know you're sensitive about that.

134
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:35,800
我才没有敏感 我只是不知道他是什么人
I'm not sensitive about it. I just don't know who he is.

135
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:40,220
如果我看起来像是在跟大祭司调情那很抱歉
Sorry if it seemed like I was flirting with the High Priestess.

136
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:41,700
我没那个意思
I wasn't.

137
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:43,140
即使你有我也不在意
I don't care if you were.

138
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:45,560
我觉得你在意
Well, I feel like you do care.

139
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,700
所以我在道歉 对不起
That's why I'm apologizing. So, sorry!

140
00:13:48,940 --> 00:13:51,220
卡魔拉不适合你 奎尔
Gamora is not the one for you, Quill.

141
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:52,800
