Damn shadow.

142
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:55,120
宇宙中有两种人
There are two types of beings in the universe...

143
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:58,100
一种是跳舞的人 另一种是不跳舞的人
those who dance, and those who do not.

144
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,540
我第一次见到我的爱人是在一场战争集会上
I first met my beloved at a war rally.

145
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:02,450
天哪
Oh, God.

146
00:14:02,450 --> 00:14:05,820
村子里每个人都在跳舞
Everyone in the village flailed about, dancing.

147
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:07,200
除了一个女人
Except one woman.

148
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,970
我的奥薇特
My Ovette.

149
00:14:09,850 --> 00:14:12,140
我立刻就知道她是我的真命天女
I knew immediately she was the one for me.

150
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:14,990
即使听着最有旋律的音乐
The most melodic song in the world could be playing.

151
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:17,520
