and I hate you.

162
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,220
你恨我
You hate me?

163
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:51,260
你丢下了我 自己去偷那块石头了
You left me there while you stole that stone for yourself.

164
00:14:51,410 --> 00:14:53,850
