and I will kill you.

167
00:14:57,350 --> 00:14:58,330
我发誓
I swear.

168
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,280
不
No.

169
00:14:59,860 --> 00:15:01,440
你会在山达尔的监狱里
You're gonna live out the rest of your days

170
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,780
