in a prison on Xandar...

171
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:05,290
做那个白日梦
wishing you could.

172
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:12,440
奇怪
This is weird.

173
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,550
有一队索维林飞船从后面追上来了
We've got a Sovereign fleet approaching from the rear.

174
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,650
他们为什么要这样
Why would they do that?

175
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:17,560
可能是因为火箭偷了他们几个电池
Probably because Rocket stole some of their batteries.

176
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,570
老兄
Dude!

177
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,870
哦
Right.

178
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,480
他没偷电池
He didn't steal some of those.

179
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,670
我不知道他们为什么追我们 真奇怪啊
I don't know why they're after us. What a mystery this is.

180
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,850
你怎么想的
What were you thinking?

181
00:15:35,850 --> 00:15:37,790
哥们 那些电池真的很容易偷
Dude, they were really easy to steal!

182
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,270
- 这就是你的辩解  - 拜托
- That's your defense?  - Come on!

183
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:41,820
你看到那个大祭司高高在上的样子了
You saw how that High Priestess talked down to us.

184
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:43,490
我这是在教训她
Now I'm teaching her a lesson!

185
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:47,020
我没想到你的动机这么无私
I didn't realize your motivation was altruism.

186
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:48,090
真是遗憾啊
It's really a shame

187
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:49,500
那些索维林人没领会到你的好意
the Sovereign have mistaken your intentions...

188
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:51,410
- 还想杀掉我们  - 说的太对了
- and they're trying to kill us.  - Exactly!

189
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:53,260
