I wanna kill some guys!

196
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,430
你谁也没杀掉
You're not killing anyone.

197
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:15,400
这些飞船都是遥控驾驶的
All those ships are remotely piloted.

198
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:19,620
该死
Damn it!

199
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:32,180
在磨蹭什么 舰队司令
What is the delay, Admiral?

200
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,120
大祭司 那些电池
High Priestess, the batteries,

201
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,120
