What's the nearest habitable planet?

209
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,330
是一个叫博赫特的星球
It's called Berhert.

210
00:17:07,330 --> 00:17:09,340
- 需要几次星际跳跃  - 只要一次
- How many jumps?  - Only one.

211
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:11,840
