instead of what's between your legs!

274
00:22:28,390 --> 00:22:31,340
如果我下面那个长了手
If what's between my legs had a hand on it...

275
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,340
那我绝对可以用它来降落飞船
I guarantee I could have landed this ship with it.

276
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:34,160
彼得
Peter,

277
00:22:34,710 --> 00:22:36,330
我们差点被你的傲慢害死
we almost died because of your arrogance.

278
00:22:36,330 --> 00:22:39,730
是因为他偷能量电池还差不多
More like because he stole the Anulax batteries!

279
00:22:39,730 --> 00:22:42,100
那个叫棱酿电池
They're called Harbulary batteries.

280
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,500
不 不叫那个
No, they're not!

281
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,970
你知道我为什么那么做吗 星嚼
Do you know why I did it, Star-Munch?

282
00:22:46,250 --> 00:22:47,670
