Well, if he got closer, I'm sure he would be much larger.

291
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:05,360
那叫近大远小 你个傻浣熊
That's how eyesight works, you stupid raccoon.

292
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:07,100
别叫我浣熊
Don't call me a raccoon!

293
00:23:07,340 --> 00:23:09,660
抱歉 是我过分了
I'm sorry. I took it too far.

294
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:12,120
我是想说垃圾熊猫
I meant trash panda.

295
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:15,310
那样好听点吗
Is that better?

296
00:23:15,930 --> 00:23:16,840
我不知道
I don't know.

297
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:20,200
这个更损 这个损多了
It's worse. It's so much worse.

298
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,650
你个混蛋
You son of a...

299
00:23:22,250 --> 00:23:23,950
- 我受够你了  - 别过来
- I've had it with you!  - No! Back up!

300
00:23:23,950 --> 00:23:25,980
有人从跳跃点跟着你们来了
Someone followed you through the jump point.

301
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:30,160
放了我 你们需要我帮忙
Set me free, you'll need my help.

302
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:31,000
我又不傻 星云
I'm not a fool, Nebula.

303
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:33,090
如果在战斗中拒绝帮助就是犯傻
You are a fool if you deprive yourself a hand in combat.

304
00:23:33,090 --> 00:23:34,860
我一放了你 你就会攻击我的
You'll attack me the moment I let you go.

305
00:23:34,860 --> 00:23:35,660
我不会的
No, I won't.

306
00:23:35,660 --> 00:23:39,200
你这种超级大坏蛋不是应该很会说谎吗
You'd think an evil supervillain would learn how to properly lie.

307
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,210
我赌是那个一英寸的小人
I bet it's the one-inch man.

308
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:16,670
时隔这么多年 我终于找到你了
After all these years, I've found you.

309
00:24:17,860 --> 00:24:19,280
你到底是谁
And who the hell are you?

310
00:24:20,260 --> 00:24:23,260
我以为我沧桑帅气的外表就足以说明了
I figured my rugged good looks would make that obvious.

311
00:24:24,970 --> 00:24:26,550
我叫伊戈
My name is Ego...

312
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,140
我是你爸爸 彼得
and I'm your dad, Peter.

313
00:24:34,700 --> 00:24:38,460
[康特阿克夏星]

314
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,600
你知道俗话怎么说的
You know what they say...

315
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:50,330
“跟过鸭鸭 好运就来”
"You're out of luck until you've gone duck."

316
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:18,320
勇度
Yondu!

317
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:21,350
快下来
Come on down!

318
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:36,140
兜兜转转这么多年
After going around years in circles...

319
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:37,680
跟我最终娶的这女人周旋
with this woman I end up marrying.

320
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:40,440
我说 “艾丽塔 我爱你
I said, "Aleta, I love you, girl...

321
00:25:40,590 --> 00:25:42,030
但你真是疯了”
"But you're losing your mind!"

322
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:44,030
话说回来 她一直都那样
Then again, she's always been that way.

323
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,710
我从来都不能相信她
I could never trust her. You know?

324
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,390
斯塔卡
Stakar.

325
00:25:51,470 --> 00:25:52,790
好久不见
It's been some time.

326
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:59,170
看来这个场子
It seems like this establishment

327
00:25:59,170 --> 00:26:01,520
堕落错了方式
is the wrong kind of disreputable.

328
00:26:07,570 --> 00:26:08,510
- 先生  - 斯塔卡
- Sir!  - Stakar!

329
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:10,860
掠夺者有一百个派系
There's a hundred Ravager factions.

330
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:14,190
你为了接待其中一个 而失去了剩下九十九个的
You lost the business of 99 of them by serving one.

331
00:26:14,190 --> 00:26:15,840
求你了 先生 别走
Please, sir. Please!

332
00:26:15,840 --> 00:26:17,650
- 别碰我  - 求你
- Get away from me.  - Please!

333
00:26:22,410 --> 00:26:24,800
你下地狱吧
You can go to hell then!

334
00:26:25,530 --> 00:26:27,940
我不在乎你怎么看我
I don't give a damn what you think of me!

335
00:26:27,940 --> 00:26:29,690
那你跟着我们干什么
So what are you following us for?

336
00:26:29,690 --> 00:26:31,320
因为你必须听我说
Because you're gonna listen to what I gotta say!

337
00:26:31,320 --> 00:26:34,550
我什么都不用听 是你背叛了准则
I don't gotta listen to nothing! You betrayed the code!

338
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:36,590
掠夺者不买卖孩子
Ravagers don't deal in kids.

339
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:39,370
我告诉过你 我不知道是怎么回事
I told you before! I didn't know what was going on!

340
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:40,140
你不知道
You didn't know

341
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:41,120
是因为你不想知道
because you didn't want to know

342
00:26:41,120 --> 00:26:42,200
因为你靠这个发财
because it made you rich.

343
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:46,900
我要求有一席之地 我跟你们一样佩戴焰标
I demand a seat at the table! I wear these flames, same as you.

344
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:48,330
你虽然穿得像我们
You may dress like us...

345
00:26:48,390 --> 00:26:51,420
但你死后别想听到自由号角声 勇度
but you'll never hear the Horns of Freedom when you die, Yondu.

346
00:26:51,890 --> 00:26:53,770
奥戈尔的颜色
And the Colors of Ogord...

347
00:26:53,910 --> 00:26:56,740
也绝不会在你的墓上闪耀
will never flash over your grave.

348
00:26:58,320 --> 00:26:59,620
要是你觉得
If you think...

349
00:27:00,970 --> 00:27:04,180
流放你 让我高兴
I take pleasure in exiling you...

350
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,770
那你就错了
you're wrong.

351
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,810
你伤了我们所有人的心
You broke all our hearts.

352
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,150
可悲
Pathetic.

353
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:31,890
起先 奎尔背叛了我们
First, Quill betrays us...

354
00:27:31,890 --> 00:27:35,130
结果勇度把他毫发无伤地放走了
and Yondu just lets him go scot-free.

355
00:27:35,630 --> 00:27:38,140
我们跟随他 是因为他
We followed him because he was the one

356
00:27:38,140 --> 00:27:40,890
敢做不得不做的事
who wasn't afraid to do what needed to be done.

357
00:27:41,470 --> 00:27:43,330
看来他变软弱了
Seems he's goin' soft.

358
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,990
要是他软弱 你这么小声干吗
If he's so soft, why are you whispering for?

359
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:49,360
你知道我说得对 克拉林
You know I'm right, Kraglin.

360
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:53,620
小心点 怎么说我们船长呢
You best be very careful what you say about our captain.

361
00:27:53,620 --> 00:27:55,350
这是谁
Who the hell is that?

362
00:28:35,430 --> 00:28:37,360
勇度·尤冬塔
Yondu Udonta...

363
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,870
我有个提议
I have a proposition for you.

364
00:28:40,670 --> 00:28:42,930
你母亲去世后
I hired Yondu to pick you up

365
00:28:42,930 --> 00:28:44,780
我雇了勇度去接你
when your mother passed away.

366
00:28:44,990 --> 00:28:46,930
但他没有把你还给我
But instead of returning you...

367
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,420
而是把你留下了
Yondu kept you.

368
00:28:48,930 --> 00:28:51,150
我不知道为什么
I have no clue as to why.

369
00:28:52,740 --> 00:28:53,930
我告诉你为什么
Well, I'll tell you why.

370
00:28:54,350 --> 00:28:55,620
因为我是个瘦得皮包骨的小孩
Because I was a skinny little kid

371
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:57,320
能溜进成年人进不去的地方
who could squeeze into places adults couldn't.

372
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:59,010
偷东西更容易
It made it easier for thievin'.

373
00:28:59,010 --> 00:29:02,440
从那时起 我就一直在寻找你的下落
Well, I've been trying to track you down ever since.

374
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:04,370
我还以为勇度是你父亲
I thought Yondu was your father.

375
00:29:04,630 --> 00:29:06,740
什么 我们在一起这么久
What? We've been together this whole time

376
00:29:06,740 --> 00:29:09,370
你以为勇度是我的血亲
and you thought Yondu was my actual blood relative?

377
00:29:09,750 --> 00:29:11,180
你俩长得一模一样
You look exactly alike.

378
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:12,800
勇度是蓝的
One's blue!

379
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:16,280
不 他不是我父亲
No, he's not my father!

380
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:18,370
勇度绑架了我
Yondu was the guy who abducted me

381
00:29:18,370 --> 00:29:20,520
把我打得满地找牙 让我学会怎么打架
kicked the crap out of me so I could learn to fight

382
00:29:20,530 --> 00:29:23,150
威胁要吃了我 让我一直担惊受怕
and kept me in terror by threatening to eat me.

383
00:29:23,150 --> 00:29:24,720
- 吃了你  - 是啊
- Eat you?  - Yeah.

384
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,580
那个王八蛋
That son of a bitch.

385
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:28,340
你怎么找到我们的
How'd you locate us now?

386
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:31,960
哪怕像我住得那么偏僻
Even where I reside, out past the edge of what's known

387
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:34,770
也听说过传说中的星爵
we've heard tell about the man they call Star-Lord.

388
00:29:34,770 --> 00:29:36,660
我们现在就出发去那儿怎么样
What say we head out there right now?

389
00:29:36,660 --> 00:29:38,200
欢迎你的伙伴一起去
Your associates are welcome.

390
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,220
包括那只三角脸猴子
Even that triangle-faced monkey there.

391
00:29:40,710 --> 00:29:41,780
我保证
I promise you...

392
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:44,640
那是一个与众不同的地方
it's unlike any other place you've ever seen.

393
00:29:45,250 --> 00:29:46,120
在那里
And there...

394
00:29:46,670 --> 00:29:51,040
我能给你解释你特别的身世
I can explain your very special heritage.

395
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:53,590
终于能做
Finally get to be the...

396
00:29:53,590 --> 00:29:55,580
我一直想做的那个父亲了
father I've always wanted to be.

397
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,020
失陪了
Excuse me.

398
00:30:00,170 --> 00:30:01,370
我去撒泡尿
I've gotta take a whiz.

399
00:30:07,670 --> 00:30:08,880
我不信
I'm not buying it.

400
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:12,830
我们去散步吧
Let's go take a walk.

401
00:30:19,970 --> 00:30:21,510
我叫螳螂
I am Mantis.

402
00:30:25,490 --> 00:30:26,520
你在干什么
What are you doing?

403
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,040
微笑
Smiling.

404
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:32,130
我听说 这样做能让人们喜欢你
I hear it is the thing to do to make people like you.

405
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,270
你那么笑可不能
Not if you do it like that.

406
00:30:36,390 --> 00:30:39,320
我一个人在伊戈的星球上长大
I was raised alone on Ego's planet.

407
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:43,300
我不了解人际交流的微妙
I do not understand the intricacies of social interaction.

408
00:30:45,810 --> 00:30:48,940
我能摸摸你的狗狗吗 它好可爱
Can I pet your puppy? It is adorable.

409
00:30:52,690 --> 00:30:53,460
可以
Yes.

410
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:06,610
这叫恶作剧
That is called a practical joke!

411
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:12,090
我很喜欢
I liked it very much!

412
00:31:12,540 --> 00:31:14,240
是我刚想的
I just made it up!

413
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:18,460
饶了我吧
Give me a break!

414
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,020
都过了这么久了 突然出现
After all this time, you're gonna show up,

415
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:22,830
- 还突然要当我爸  - 是啊
- and just all of a sudden you wanna be my dad?  - I hear you.

416
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:25,190
另外 这可能是个陷阱 好吗
And by the way, this could be a trap. Okay?

417
00:31:25,190 --> 00:31:26,910
克里纯种主义者 掠夺者
The Kree purists, the Ravagers...

418
00:31:26,910 --> 00:31:28,990
- 都想杀死我们  - 我知道 但是…
- they all want us dead.  - I know, but...

419
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:29,910
但是什么
But what?

420
00:31:29,910 --> 00:31:32,710
你给我讲的扎渡·霍索妇的故事呢
What was that story you told me about Zardu Hasselfrau?

421
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:33,570
谁
Who?

422
00:31:33,780 --> 00:31:35,260
有一艘魔法船的那个
He owned a magic boat?

423
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:38,310
大卫·霍索夫
David Hasselhoff?

424
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:38,940
就是他
Right.

425
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:41,440
不是魔法船 是会说话的车
Not a magic boat. A talking car.

426
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,720
为什么会说话来着
Why did he talk again?

427
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:46,200
为了帮他打击犯罪 并给予精神支持
To help him fight crime, and to be supportive.

428
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,940
你小时候会随身带着他的照片
As a child, you would carry his picture in your pocket

429
00:31:48,950 --> 00:31:50,970
告诉其他小孩
and you would tell all the other children

430
00:31:50,970 --> 00:31:53,410
说他是你父亲 但他出门了
that he was your father, but that he was out of town.

431
00:31:53,410 --> 00:31:56,010
拍摄《霹雳游侠》或者跟乐队在德国巡回演出
Shooting Knight Rider or touring with his band in Germany.

432
00:31:56,010 --> 00:31:57,380
那是我喝醉时告诉你的
I told you that when I was drunk.

433
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:58,600
你现在提它干吗
Why are you bringing that up now?

434
00:31:58,600 --> 00:31:59,820
我喜欢那个故事
I love that story.

435
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:01,640
我讨厌那个故事
I hate that story.

436
00:32:01,940 --> 00:32:03,350
太可悲了
It's so sad!

437
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:06,440
我小时候总是看着其他孩子
As a kid, I used to see all the other kids off

438
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:08,600
跟他们的爸爸玩投接球
playing catch with their dad. And I

439
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:11,690
我也想让爸爸陪我玩 那是我最大的心愿
I wanted that, more than anything in the world!

440
00:32:11,740 --> 00:32:13,530
我就想说这个 彼得
That's my point, Peter.

441
00:32:14,630 --> 00:32:17,770
如果这个人就是你的霍索夫呢
What if this man is your Hasselhoff?

442
00:32:20,120 --> 00:32:22,870
听着 如果我们发现他是坏人
Listen, if he ends up being evil...

443
00:32:24,050 --> 00:32:25,130
那就杀了他
we will just kill him.

444
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,240
你要把我丢给那只狐狸
You're leaving me with that fox?

445
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:36,560
他不是狐狸
He's not a fox.

446
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:38,780
要是她行为可疑 就开枪打她
Shoot her if she does anything suspicious.

447
00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:41,710
- 或者你想打就打  - 好
- Or if you feel like it.  - Okay.

448
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:45,120
就几天而已
It'll be just a couple of days.

449
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:47,740
还没等火箭修好飞船 我们就能回来了
We'll be back before Rocket's finished fixing the ship.

450
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:53,290
要是索维林人来了怎么办
What if the Sovereign come?

451
00:32:53,290 --> 00:32:55,610
他们不可能知道我们在这儿 走吧
There's no way for them to know we're here. Let's go.

452
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:57,850
我觉得兵分两路不太好
I'm uncertain about parting ways.

453
00:32:57,850 --> 00:32:59,240
天啊 你就像个老太婆
God, you're like an old woman.

454
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:00,980
因为我睿智吗
Because I'm wise?

455
00:33:02,120 --> 00:33:04,060
你怎么有这么多行李
Why do you have so much luggage?

456
00:33:04,090 --> 00:33:06,030
我不想让格鲁特乱动我的东西
I don't want Groot playing with my things.

457
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:12,950
希望老爸不像你那么混蛋 小孤儿
I hope Daddy isn't as big of a dick as you, orphan boy.

458
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:18,520
你的目的是什么 让所有人都讨厌你吗
What is your goal here? To get everybody to hate you?

459
00:33:19,050 --> 00:33:20,320
你成功了
Because it's working.

460
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:10,150
我能问你个私人问题吗
Hey, can I ask you a personal question?

461
00:34:12,250 --> 00:34:15,070
还没人问过我私人问题呢
No one has ever asked me a personal question.

462
00:34:15,070 --> 00:34:16,710
你的触角是干什么的
Your antennae, what are they for?

463
00:34:17,370 --> 00:34:18,460
触角的用途
Their purpose?

464
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:20,420
对 奎尔和我打了个赌
Yes. Quill and I have a bet.

465
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:23,310
哥们 你不应该说出来的
Dude. You're not supposed to say that!

466
00:34:23,590 --> 00:34:24,530
我说
I say...

467
00:34:24,530 --> 00:34:27,160
当你要穿过一个很低的门框时
that if you are about to go through a doorway that is too low...

468
00:34:27,370 --> 00:34:28,730
你的触角能感知高度
your antennae will feel this,

469
00:34:28,730 --> 00:34:30,350
防止你撞掉脑袋
and keep you from being decapitated.

470
00:34:30,350 --> 00:34:32,060
对 如果是任何
Right. And if it's anything other than

471
00:34:32,060 --> 00:34:36,090
防止掉脑袋之外的用途 那我赢
you specifically not being decapitated by a doorway, I win.

472
00:34:36,090 --> 00:34:39,420
它们不是感知门框用的
They are not for feeling doorways.

473
00:34:40,540 --> 00:34:41,560
我觉得
I think...

474
00:34:41,890 --> 00:34:45,020
它们跟我的共情能力有关
they have something to do with my empathic abilities.

475
00:34:45,160 --> 00:34:46,190
那是什么
What are those?

476
00:34:46,350 --> 00:34:50,410
我触碰别人时 我能感觉到他们的感受
If I touch someone, I can feel their feelings.

477
00:34:50,570 --> 00:34:52,470
- 你会读心术  - 不是
- You read minds?  - No.

478
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:54,740
心灵感应是感知想法
Telepaths know thoughts.

479
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:57,390
共情是感知感情
Empaths feel feelings.

480
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:00,220
情绪
Emotions.

481
00:35:02,390 --> 00:35:03,210
可以吗
May I?

482
00:35:04,720 --> 00:35:05,700
好
All right.

483
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:17,030
你怀着爱
You feel love.

484
00:35:18,490 --> 00:35:20,320
是的 我怀着一种
Yeah. I guess I feel a general,

485
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:22,730
- 对所有人的无私的大爱  - 不
- unselfish love for just about everybody.  - No!

486
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:25,200
是浪漫的 肉欲的爱
Romantic, sexual love.

487
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:26,390
我才没
