00:51:42,850 --> 00:51:44,810
或会说话的森林野兽那么好对付
or a talking woodland beast.

681
00:51:46,270 --> 00:51:47,990
我要百分之十的赏金
I want 10% of the take...

682
00:51:49,900 --> 00:51:51,660
还有几样东西
and a couple more things.

683
00:51:53,440 --> 00:51:54,920
我们有一整盒的手
We got a whole box of hands...

684
00:51:54,920 --> 00:51:57,320
- 如果那个不行的话  - 挺好的
- if that one don't work out.  - It is fine.

685
00:51:57,320 --> 00:52:00,460
你觉得克里人会处死船长吗
You think them Kree is gonna execute the captain?

686
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:04,170
克里人自视仁慈 不会让他痛苦的
The Kree consider themselves merciful. It will be painless.

687
00:52:05,010 --> 00:52:08,460
就在这儿 这是我们最好的一艘船
Well, here it is. It's the best ship we got.

688
00:52:08,700 --> 00:52:10,460
伊戈星球的位置发到导航里了
Location of Ego's planet in the nav.

689
00:52:10,460 --> 00:52:12,700
等我们拿到钱就把那百分之十汇给你
We'll wire you the 10% once we's paid.

690
00:52:13,160 --> 00:52:14,780
你打算拿你的那份做什么
What are you gonna do with your share?

691
00:52:16,020 --> 00:52:17,210
我还是孩子时 我父亲会让
As a child, my father would have

692
00:52:17,210 --> 00:52:19,770
我和卡魔拉在训练中对打
Gamora and me battle one another in training.

693
00:52:20,960 --> 00:52:23,050
每次我姐姐赢了
Every time my sister prevailed

694
00:52:23,450 --> 00:52:26,160
我父亲就会把我身体的一部分换成机械
my father would replace a piece of me with machinery

695
00:52:26,850 --> 00:52:29,470
他说是希望我能像她一样强
claiming he wanted me to be her equal.

696
00:52:30,840 --> 00:52:31,930
但她总赢
But she won...

697
00:52:32,700 --> 00:52:37,790
一次又一次 从没一次手下留情
again and again, and again, never once refraining.

698
00:52:39,050 --> 00:52:40,880
所以等我杀了我姐姐
So after I murder my sister...

699
00:52:41,740 --> 00:52:45,080
我要买一艘战舰 装上所有杀戮武器
I will buy a warship with every conceivable instrument of death.

700
00:52:45,080 --> 00:52:46,510
我要像抓狗一样找到我父亲
I will hunt my father like a dog,

701
00:52:46,510 --> 00:52:48,680
然后慢慢把他撕碎
and I will tear him apart slowly

702
00:52:48,870 --> 00:52:50,390
一块一块地拆开
piece by piece...

703
00:52:50,390 --> 00:52:54,010
直到他能稍有体会我每一天所经历的
until he knows some semblance of the profound and unceasing pain

704
00:52:54,010 --> 00:52:57,100
无休止的深刻痛苦
I know every single day.

705
00:52:58,960 --> 00:53:00,050
哦
Yeah.

706
00:53:00,780 --> 00:53:02,900
我想的是买条漂亮项链什么的
I was talking about, like, a pretty necklace.

707
00:53:03,540 --> 00:53:05,220
或是好看的帽子
Or a nice hat. You know,

708
00:53:05,270 --> 00:53:08,650
让其他姑娘都说“哎呀 真漂亮”
something to make the other girls go, "Ooh, that's nice!"

709
00:53:12,040 --> 00:53:15,060
总之 一路顺风
Anyways, happy trails.

710
00:53:23,150 --> 00:53:26,240
我母亲跟所有人说我父亲来自星星
My mother told everyone my father was from the stars.

711
00:53:28,440 --> 00:53:30,970
她有脑瘤 所以大家都以为她是在妄想
She had brain cancer, so everyone thought she was delusional.

712
00:53:30,970 --> 00:53:31,810
彼得
Peter...

713
00:53:31,930 --> 00:53:34,400
听着 我真的很想相信这一切
Listen, I'd love to believe all of this, I really would.

714
00:53:34,400 --> 00:53:38,380
但你离开了这世上最棒的女人
But you left the most wonderful woman ever

715
00:53:38,850 --> 00:53:40,190
让她孤独离世
to die alone.

716
00:53:40,190 --> 00:53:43,720
我并不想离开你母亲的 彼得
I didn't want to leave your mother, Peter.

717
00:53:43,790 --> 00:53:46,350
如果我不定期回到我的星球
If I don't return regularly to my planet

718
00:53:46,350 --> 00:53:47,760
回归其内部的光
and the light within it

719
00:53:47,810 --> 00:53:49,370
这个人形将退化消逝
this form will wither and perish.

720
00:53:49,370 --> 00:53:51,720
那你为什么不回来 你为什么叫勇度去
So why didn't you come back? Why did you send Yondu?

721
00:53:51,720 --> 00:53:53,980
偏偏叫一个罪犯去接我
A criminal, of all people, to come and fetch me?

722
00:53:53,980 --> 00:53:56,110
我是那么爱你母亲 彼得
I loved your mother, Peter!

723
00:53:56,110 --> 00:54:00,120
我无法忍受去一个再没有她的地球
I couldn't stand to set foot on an Earth where she wasn't living!

724
00:54:00,120 --> 00:54:01,410
你无法想象那是什么感觉
You can't imagine what that's like!

725
00:54:01,410 --> 00:54:03,670
我非常清楚那是什么感觉
I know exactly what that feels like!

726
00:54:04,220 --> 00:54:06,010
我不得不看着她死去
I had to watch her die!

727
00:54:10,480 --> 00:54:14,820
我存在了千百万年
Over the millions and millions of years of my existence

728
00:54:14,820 --> 00:54:17,000
犯下了很多错误 彼得
I've made many mistakes, Peter.

729
00:54:18,020 --> 00:54:19,800
但你不是其中之一
But you're not one of them.

730
00:54:21,900 --> 00:54:23,310
请给我个机会
Please give me the chance

731
00:54:23,310 --> 00:54:25,590
做她会希望我做的那种父亲
to be the father she would want me to be.

732
00:54:30,470 --> 00:54:35,460
关于这个星球 和其内部的光
There's so much that I need to teach you about this planet

733
00:54:36,190 --> 00:54:37,520
我有好多要告诉你
and the light within.

734
00:54:38,010 --> 00:54:40,460
那是你的一部分 彼得
They are a part of you, Peter.

735
00:54:42,130 --> 00:54:42,970
什么意思
What do you mean?

736
00:54:44,570 --> 00:54:45,920
给我你的手 儿子
Give me your hands, son.

737
00:54:47,470 --> 00:54:48,220
来
Here.

738
00:54:49,550 --> 00:54:50,920
这样端住
Hold them like that.

739
00:54:54,240 --> 00:54:54,980
好了
Now,

740
00:54:57,220 --> 00:54:59,780
闭上眼睛 集中精神
close your eyes and concentrate.

741
00:55:01,480 --> 00:55:03,690
让思绪进入星球的中心
Take your brain to the center of this planet.

742
00:55:09,020 --> 00:55:10,100
太好了
Yes!

743
00:55:10,470 --> 00:55:11,370
就这样
Yes!

744
00:55:11,870 --> 00:55:13,050
太好了
Yes! Yes!

745
00:55:13,270 --> 00:55:14,570
- 太棒了 没事  - 怎么回…
- Yes! It's okay.  - What was...

746
00:55:14,570 --> 00:55:16,170
放松 集中精神
Just relax. Concentrate.

747
00:55:16,170 --> 00:55:17,890
你可以的 再来
You can do it. Bring it back.

748
00:55:18,730 --> 00:55:19,630
很好
Yes!

749
00:55:21,050 --> 00:55:24,140
很好 好了 塑形
Yes, yes, now shape it.

750
00:55:24,520 --> 00:55:25,800
感受那股能量
Feel that energy.

751
00:55:30,520 --> 00:55:31,550
就这样
Yes.

752
00:55:35,800 --> 00:55:36,730
你回家了
You're home.

753
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:40,560
彼得
Peter...

754
00:56:15,270 --> 00:56:18,180
你是怎么来到这颗奇怪 愚蠢的星球上的
How did you get to this weird, dumb planet?

755
00:56:18,990 --> 00:56:21,230
我还是个幼虫时被伊戈发现
Ego found me in my larva state.

756
00:56:21,500 --> 00:56:23,520
我在母星是个孤儿
Orphaned on my homeworld.

757
00:56:24,570 --> 00:56:27,810
他亲手养大了我 把我留在了身边
He raised me by hand, and kept me as his own.

758
00:56:28,610 --> 00:56:30,090
那么你是个宠物
So you're a pet?

759
00:56:31,140 --> 00:56:32,450
大概是吧
I suppose.

760
00:56:33,980 --> 00:56:35,940
人们一般都养可爱的宠物
People usually want cute pets.

761
00:56:36,470 --> 00:56:38,540
伊戈怎么会养个这么面目可憎的
Why would Ego want such a hideous one?

762
00:56:39,010 --> 00:56:40,290
我面目可憎吗
I am hideous?

763
00:56:40,290 --> 00:56:43,020
你简直丑得惊心动魄
You are horrifying to look at. Yes.

764
00:56:45,700 --> 00:56:47,140
但那是好事
But that's a good thing.

765
00:56:48,380 --> 00:56:50,000
如果你长得丑 还有人爱你
When you're ugly, and someone loves you

766
00:56:50,000 --> 00:56:51,940
你知道那人是爱你这个人
you know they love you for who you are.

767
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:56,400
美丽的人永远不知道谁能信任
Beautiful people never know who to trust.

768
00:56:56,400 --> 00:56:59,700
那我庆幸我很丑
Well, then I'm certainly grateful to be ugly.

769
00:57:01,670 --> 00:57:04,890
那些池塘 让我想起了有次
Those pools, they remind me of a time...

770
00:57:04,890 --> 00:57:08,340
我带女儿去我母星的遗忘湖
when I took my daughter to the forgotten lakes of my homeworld.

771
00:57:09,830 --> 00:57:11,200
她跟你很像
She was like you.

772
00:57:11,500 --> 00:57:12,710
难看吗
Disgusting?

773
00:57:14,020 --> 00:57:15,010
天真无邪
Innocent.

774
00:57:48,760 --> 00:57:49,860
德拉克斯
Drax?

775
00:57:50,740 --> 00:57:52,610
我得告诉你件事
There's something I must tell you.

776
00:58:01,360 --> 00:58:02,100
怎么回事
What's going on?

777
00:58:02,110 --> 00:58:04,420
这位恶心的虫子女士成了我的新朋友
This gross bug lady is my new friend.

778
00:58:04,420 --> 00:58:07,560
我学到了很多事 比如我是个宠物 而且很丑
I'm learning many things, like I'm a pet and ugly.

779
00:58:08,400 --> 00:58:10,200
你不丑 德拉克斯
You're not ugly. Drax!

780
00:58:10,200 --> 00:58:11,360
你说什么呢
What are you talking about?

781
00:58:11,360 --> 00:58:12,370
螳螂
Mantis...

782
00:58:12,610 --> 00:58:14,630
你能带我们去我们的住处吗
can you show us where we'll be staying?

783
00:58:15,820 --> 00:58:17,650
这颗星球上怎么没有其他生物
Why are there no other beings on this planet?

784
00:58:17,650 --> 00:58:19,770
这星球就是伊戈
The planet is Ego.

785
00:58:19,970 --> 00:58:22,900
狗不会邀请跳蚤来他背上住
A dog would not invite a flea to live on his back.

786
00:58:23,020 --> 00:58:24,370
你不是跳蚤
And you're not a flea?

787
00:58:24,560 --> 00:58:26,320
我是有用的跳蚤
I'm a flea with a purpose.

788
00:58:27,360 --> 00:58:28,820
我帮他入眠
I help him sleep.

789
00:58:30,050 --> 00:58:33,150
我走出来之前 你正要跟德拉克斯说什么
What were you about to say to Drax before I walked out?

790
00:58:38,450 --> 00:58:39,430
没什么
Nothing.

791
00:58:40,270 --> 00:58:42,040
你们的住处在这边
Your quarters are this way.

792
00:58:49,900 --> 00:58:52,420
我们明早把你们送去给克里人
We deliver you to the Kree in the morning.

793
00:58:55,590 --> 00:58:58,560
之后你俩都活不长了
Neither one of you will last much longer after that.

794
00:58:59,510 --> 00:59:01,180
好啊 电击脸
Okay, Taserface.

795
00:59:02,470 --> 00:59:06,020
替我们跟其他人问好 电击脸
Tell the other guys we said "Hi," Taserface!

796
00:59:11,350 --> 00:59:13,710
这颗小植物呢 要我用石头砸碎它吗
What about this little plant? Can I smash it with a rock?

797
00:59:13,710 --> 00:59:15,200
不行 杰夫
No, Gef.

798
00:59:15,200 --> 00:59:16,910
这么可爱怎么能杀掉
It's too adorable to kill.

799
00:59:17,290 --> 00:59:18,680
送去裁缝那里
Take it to the tailor.

800
00:59:20,560 --> 00:59:23,640
别介意 但你的雇员都是混蛋
No offense, but your employees are a bunch of jerks.

801
00:59:26,400 --> 00:59:31,310
我做了二十年的克里人战奴 是斯塔卡解救了我
I was a Kree battle slave for 20 years when Stakar freed me.

802
00:59:33,180 --> 00:59:35,790
他邀我加入了掠夺者
He offered me a place with the Ravagers.

803
00:59:36,500 --> 00:59:40,020
他说我只需要遵守准则
He said all I needed to do was adhere to the code.

804
00:59:41,190 --> 00:59:42,620
但我年轻
But I was young...

805
00:59:43,970 --> 00:59:47,240
贪心 愚蠢
and greedy, and stupid.

806
00:59:48,230 --> 00:59:50,390
就像你 偷了那些电池
Like you stealing those batteries.

807
00:59:50,390 --> 00:59:52,060
那更多是德拉克斯干的
That was mostly Drax.

808
00:59:53,670 --> 00:59:56,530
我和斯塔卡 还有其他船长
Me and Stakar and the other captains...

809
00:59:58,070 --> 01:00:00,480
我们跟你和你的朋友很像
we weren't so different from you and your friends.

810
01:00:01,420 --> 01:00:03,400
那是我唯一的家庭
The only family I ever had.

811
01:00:04,390 --> 01:00:06,130
我违反准则后
When I broke the code...

812
01:00:08,640 --> 01:00:09,990
他们流放了我
they exiled me.

813
01:00:11,640 --> 01:00:13,180
我活该如此
This is what I deserve.

814
01:00:13,180 --> 01:00:15,190
等等 矫情女王
Slow down, drama queen.

815
01:00:15,190 --> 01:00:16,750
你或许是活该 但我不是
You might deserve this, but I don't.

816
01:00:16,750 --> 01:00:18,150
我们得逃出去
We gotta get outta here.

817
01:00:20,190 --> 01:00:21,290
奎尔呢
Where's Quill?

818
01:00:22,170 --> 01:00:23,800
他跟他老爸走了
He went off with his old man.

819
01:00:24,770 --> 01:00:26,380
- 伊戈  - 对
- Ego?  - Yeah.

820
01:00:26,740 --> 01:00:28,550
今天净是些蠢蛋名字
It's a day for dumbass names.

821
01:00:31,710 --> 01:00:34,330
你笑了 就那么一刻 我有种温暖的感觉
You're smiling. And for a second, I got a warm feeling.

822
01:00:34,330 --> 01:00:37,060
但你那一口烂牙毁了这感觉
But then it was ruined by those disgusting-ass teeth.

823
01:00:37,060 --> 01:00:39,590
你是职业混蛋吗
You like a professional asshole or what?

824
01:00:39,590 --> 01:00:40,650
挺专业的反正
Pretty much a pro.

825
01:00:40,650 --> 01:00:43,440
你为什么没像说好的那样把奎尔送去给伊戈
Why didn't you deliver Quill to Ego like you promised?

826
01:00:44,200 --> 01:00:45,450
他很瘦小
He was skinny.

827
01:00:46,170 --> 01:00:50,060
能钻进我们钻不进的地方 适合偷盗
Could fit into places we couldn't. Good for thievin'.

828
01:00:55,470 --> 01:00:57,970
我知道我们怎么出去了
I got an idea on how to get outta here.

829
01:00:59,570 --> 01:01:01,520
但我需要你的小朋友
But we're gonna need your little friend.

830
01:01:02,920 --> 01:01:05,620
吉祥物 吉祥物
Mascot, mascot, mascot...

831
01:01:16,120 --> 01:01:19,120
小家伙好激动 该喝一杯
Little fellow's all worked up! He needs a drink!

832
01:01:24,950 --> 01:01:27,850
看他气成那样多可爱
Look how cute it is when it's all riled up.

833
01:01:27,850 --> 01:01:30,200
他太有趣了
He's goddang precious!

834
01:01:43,770 --> 01:01:44,960
小树枝
Hey, twig!

835
01:01:45,890 --> 01:01:46,750
过来
Come here.

836
01:01:47,790 --> 01:01:48,640
过来
Come on.

837
01:01:56,250 --> 01:01:58,150
天呐 他们把你怎么了
Man... what did they do to you?

838
01:02:01,280 --> 01:02:03,250
你想帮我们出去吗
You wanna help us get outta here?

839
01:02:04,390 --> 01:02:07,540
我需要你去找样东西 然后拿来给我
There's something I need you to get, and bring back to me.

840
01:02:07,880 --> 01:02:12,120
在船长室 有个原型机机械鳍
In the captain's quarters, there's a prototype fin...

841
01:02:12,370 --> 01:02:14,160
就是我脑袋上戴的那玩意
the thing I wore on my head.

842
01:02:14,370 --> 01:02:18,650
床铺旁边有个抽屉 就在里面 红色的
There's a drawer next to the bunk. It's in that. It's red.

843
01:02:18,650 --> 01:02:19,650
懂了吗
You got it?

844
01:02:53,730 --> 01:02:55,370
那是我的内裤
That's my underwears.

845
01:02:55,370 --> 01:02:56,140
嗯 我就觉得
Yeah, I was pretty sure

846
01:02:56,140 --> 01:02:57,580
他根本就没听懂你说什么
he didn't know what you were talkin' about.

847
01:02:57,580 --> 01:02:59,600
你得解释得更细致点
You have to explain it more careful.

848
01:03:01,200 --> 01:03:04,690
是个原型机机械鳍
It's a prototype fin.

849
01:03:09,980 --> 01:03:12,960
那是只奥罗尼 机械鳍 格鲁特
That's an orloni. It's a fin, Groot.

850
01:03:12,960 --> 01:03:14,710
这次你来解释
You explain it this time.

851
01:03:15,820 --> 01:03:16,620
好吧
All right.

852
01:03:18,120 --> 01:03:20,180
那是沃克的眼睛
That's Vorker's eye.

853
01:03:20,180 --> 01:03:22,220
他睡觉时会拿下来
He takes it out when he sleeps.

854
01:03:22,230 --> 01:03:23,520
去 再找
Go. Look again.

855
01:03:23,520 --> 01:03:25,000
把眼睛留下
But leave the eye here.

856
01:03:25,910 --> 01:03:26,720
干吗
Why?

857
01:03:26,740 --> 01:03:28,500
等他明早醒来
He's gonna wake up tomorrow

858
01:03:28,530 --> 01:03:30,510
会不知道
and he's not gonna know

859
01:03:30,760 --> 01:03:32,820
他的眼睛去哪了
where his eye is!

860
01:03:39,400 --> 01:03:40,800
那是张桌子
That's a desk.

861
01:03:41,190 --> 01:03:43,220
我们说了那玩意才这么大
We told you it was this big.

