我赢了
I win.

966
01:17:48,940 --> 01:17:50,700
我赢了 我打败了你
I win. I bested you in combat.

967
01:17:50,700 --> 01:17:53,050
不 是我救了你
No. I saved your life.

968
01:17:53,050 --> 01:17:55,160
