It's obvious!

976
01:18:04,890 --> 01:18:08,460
你才是想赢的那个 我只想要个姐姐
You were the one who wanted to win. And I just wanted a sister!

977
01:18:16,310 --> 01:18:17,820
我只有你
You were all I had.

978
01:18:19,160 --> 01:18:21,400
但你总想赢
But you were the one who needed to win.

979
01:18:23,290 --> 01:18:25,380
灭霸把我的眼睛挖出来
Thanos pulled my eye from my head

980
01:18:26,220 --> 01:18:27,920
把我的大脑取出来
and my brain from my skull

981
01:18:29,460 --> 01:18:31,060
把我的胳膊拽下来
and my arm from my body

982
01:18:33,100 --> 01:18:34,520
都是因为你
because of you.

983
01:18:56,110 --> 01:18:57,350
你没事吧 儿子
You all right, son?

984
01:18:59,210 --> 01:19:03,580
我之前看见你女朋友怒气冲冲地走了
I saw your girl stomp off a little earlier in quite a huff.

985
01:19:03,580 --> 01:19:04,500
是啊
Yeah.

986
01:19:05,140 --> 01:19:08,150
