Thor, it's madness.

140
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:46,480
发疯  哪种程度的发疯
Madness? What sort of madness?

141
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,100
我们要去约顿海姆
We're going to Jotunheim.

142
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:50,830
什么
