You did.

155
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:22,520
沃斯塔格  是谁给了你鲜美的佳肴
And Volstagg, to delicacies so succulent,

156
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:25,060
让你觉得欲仙欲死  仿佛升入了英灵殿呢
you thought you'd died and gone to Valhalla?

157
00:14:26,770 --> 00:14:27,590
是你
You did.

158
00:14:27,590 --> 00:14:28,470
