160
00:14:30,650 --> 00:14:33,250
少女不能成为王国最威猛的战士的人
that a young maiden could be one of the fiercest warriors

161
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:34,600
证明了他们的错误呢
this realm has ever known?

162
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:35,660
是我
I did.

163
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,810
的确  但我一直支持你  希芙
True, but I supported you, Sif.

164
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,350
朋友们
My friends,

165
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:42,100
我们要去约顿海姆
we're going to Jotunheim.

166
00:15:33,770 --> 00:15:34,960
交给我吧
You leave this to me.

167
