Be warned.

179
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:00,410
作为门卫
I will honor my sworn oath

180
00:17:00,410 --> 00:17:03,580
我将遵守保护王国的誓言
to protect this realm as its Gatekeeper.

181
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:06,400
如果你们的归来威胁了阿斯加德的安全
If your return threatens the safety of Asgard,

182
00:17:06,410 --> 00:17:09,080
彩虹桥将不会为你们开启
Bifrost will remain closed to you

183
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:12,560
你将被留在约顿海姆的寒冷荒漠中等死
and you'll be left to die in the cold waste of Jotunheim.

184
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,590
你不能干脆为我们一直开着桥吗
Couldn't you just leave the bridge open for us?

185
00:17:14,590 --> 00:17:15,830
一直开启
