187
00:17:18,050 --> 00:17:21,630
摧毁连你们在内的整个约顿海姆
and destroy Jotunheim with you upon it.

188
00:17:21,630 --> 00:17:23,680
我可不准备今天死
I have no plans to die today.

189
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:24,800
没人想死
None do.

190
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,890
我们不该来的
We shouldn't be here.

191
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:16,140
