You never knew him.

1483
01:41:40,550 --> 01:41:42,060
没见过他最辉煌的时刻
Not at his best.

1484
01:41:42,890 --> 01:41:47,380
奥丁和我曾让整个文明淹死在血泪之中
Odin and I drowned entire civilizations in blood and tears.

1485
