很好
Good.

1515
02:01:24,120 --> 02:01:25,800
他们不是要拆楼
They are not tearing it down.

1516
02:01:27,390 --> 02:01:28,880
我买下了这栋楼
I bought this building.

1517
02:01:31,010 --> 02:01:32,260
还有那栋楼
And that building.

1518
02:01:33,780 --> 02:01:35,080
还有那边那栋
And that one over there.

1519
02:01:36,710 --> 02:01:40,440
